data.description: DREAM home with LAKE access! This Luxury 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath Waterfront home on beautiful Haines Creek Canal with NO HOA is nestled in a country setting on a spacious 1.3-acre lot with 100 feet of canal frontage. Almost-new luxurious 2-year-old home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and serene waterfront living. Situated on the canal, which connects to the renowned Harris Chain of Lakes, this property is a boater's dream come true! This home boasts three generously sized bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The living room is adorned with a tray ceiling and elegant crown moldings throughout the home, creating an inviting and stylish atmosphere. Enjoy quality time with family and friends in the huge family room, complete with a wet bar and a cozy wood-burning fireplace – perfect for entertaining or relaxation. Fully embrace the Florida lifestyle in the sunlit screened Florida room, where you'll soak in the scenic views of the canal, your immense backyard, and nature displays. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, a gas range, a walk-in pantry, ample cabinet space, and a convenient island. Each room is equipped with ceiling fans to ensure comfortable airflow throughout the home. The property includes a 2-car carport and two utility sheds, providing storage space for your vehicles and outdoor equipment. One shed boasts a full refrigerator. This home offers the best of both worlds – a country feel on a peaceful dirt road, yet conveniently located just off County Road 44. You'll be close to shopping, dining, and all the amenities while enjoying the tranquility of waterfront living. With no homeowners' association (HOA) restrictions, and Zoned A - Agricultural, you have the freedom to make this property your very own without worrying about HOA or Residential restrictions. The 1.3 acres of land are high and dry, ensuring a secure and stable foundation for your home. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful and well-kept waterfront property with modern amenities, a spacious lot, and direct access to the Harris Chain of Lakes. Contact us today to schedule a showing, and make this dream home yours!   360° virtual tour link: https://mls.ricoh360.com/25df2217-29af-4fd2-a9db-d01a9c009103
